      "value": {
        "latex": "$S = \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^2-u^{-2}} +\n     \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^4-u^{-4}} + \\dots +\n     \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^{2^n}-u^{-2^n}}$.\n\\par\n$\\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^2-u^{-2}} +\n \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^4-u^{-4}} =\n \\frac {u^3-u^{-3}}{u^4-u^{-4}}$.\n\\par\n$\\frac {u^3-u^{-3}}{u^4-u^{-4}} +\n \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^8-u^{-8}} =\n \\frac {u^7-u^{-7}}{u^8-u^{-8}}$\n$\\ldots$\n\\par\n$ \\Rightarrow  S = \\frac {u^{2^n-1}-u^{-2^n+1}}{u^{2^n}-u^{-2^n}}\n       = \\frac {\\sin\\bigl((2^n-1)\\theta\\bigr)}{\\sin(2^n\\theta)}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(S = \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^2-u^{-2}} +\n     \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^4-u^{-4}} + \\dots +\n     \\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^{2^n}-u^{-2^n}}\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^2-u^{-2}} +\n\\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^4-u^{-4}} =\n\\frac {u^3-u^{-3}}{u^4-u^{-4}}\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {u^3-u^{-3}}{u^4-u^{-4}} +\n\\frac {u-u^{-1}}{u^8-u^{-8}} =\n\\frac {u^7-u^{-7}}{u^8-u^{-8}}\\)</span> <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\ldots\\)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rightarrow  S = \\frac\n{u^{2^n-1}-u^{-2^n+1}}{u^{2^n}-u^{-2^n}}\n       = \\frac\n{\\sin\\bigl((2^n-1)\\theta\\bigr)}{\\sin(2^n\\theta)}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
